# Related file: `src/scripts/runCLI.ts` (specifically the `lint-staged` CLI)
#
# pre-commit Git hook commands run prior to any changes being committed. Details:
# - `pnpm build`  - Build the codebase to `lib/` so that all configuration files are up-to-date.
# - `lint-staged` - Run the validation checks scoped to just the staged files.
pnpm githooks.pre-commit
